data.title: Qlik Replicate (formerly Attunity Replicate)
data.meta_description: Discover 200+ expert-built Apache Kafka connectors for seamless, real-time data streaming and integration. Connect with MongoDB, AWS S3, Snowflake, and more.
data.text: Qlik integrates data from any data source for real-time data streaming and analytics. 1As customers modernize their data centers, they use Qlik Replicateâ¢(formerly Attunity Replicate) to stream their data from multiple sources across the organization to Apache Kafka or the Confluent Platform. Qlik Replicate is a fully automated software solution with unique log-based change data capture (CDC) technology.
